creator: Instanture Holdings Sdn Bhd
descriptionHtml:
Boostorder helps you accelerate your business velocity and generate more sales.

You’ve probably faced some very tedious problems when it comes to utilising the standard, manual ordering system. For instance, you’ll often find yourself stuck with outdated product information. Also, with the lack of real-time options, you will have to wait on the edge of your seat figuring out of the state of progression of your orders.

Luckily for you, Boostorder will make the horrors of a manual ordering system a distant memory of the past. The latest product information is now at your fingertips, and you easily place an order with our mobile ordering app.
descriptionShort: Boostorder is a simple yet effective B2B e-commerce solution.

creator: Instanture Holdings Sdn Bhd
descriptionHtml:
Boostorder helps you accelerate your business velocity and generate more sales.

You’ve probably faced some very tedious problems when it comes to utilising the standard, manual ordering system. For instance, you’ll often find yourself stuck with outdated product information. Also, with the lack of real-time options, you will have to wait on the edge of your seat figuring out of the state of progression of your orders.

Luckily for you, Boostorder will make the horrors of a manual ordering system a distant memory of the past. The latest product information is now at your fingertips, and you easily place an order with our mobile ordering app.
